<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User Blocked | FloraGems</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <style>body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }
    
    .container {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        text-align: center;
    }
    
    .blocked-message {
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        width: 300px;
    }
    
    .blocked-message h1 {
        color: #e74c3c;
        font-size: 24px;
    }
    
    .blocked-message p {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    .btn {
        background-color: #3498db;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 50px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #777;
    }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="blocked-message">
            <h1>Account Blocked</h1>
            <p>We are sorry, but your account has been blocked due to violations of our terms of service. Please contact support for more information.</p>
            <p>If you believe this is a mistake, feel free to reach out to us using the contact form below.</p>
            <a href="/contact-us" class="btn">Contact Support</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 FloraGems. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
